      <title>阿萨德倒台震动伊朗日益脆弱的领导层</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/is-iran-next-fall-of-assad-jolts-a-vulnerable-leadership</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着唐纳德·特朗普准备重返白宫，伊朗伊斯兰共和国的“抵抗轴心”被打破，政权陷入混乱。]]></description>
